38/* Read a STRING_CST from the string table in DATA_IN using input
39 block IB. */
40
41tree
42streamer_read_string_cst (struct data_in *data_in, struct lto_input_block *ib)
43{
44 unsigned int len;
45 const char * ptr;
46
47 ptr = streamer_read_indexed_string (data_in, ib, &len);
48 if (!ptr)
49 return NULL;
50 return build_string (len, ptr);
51}
52
53
54/* Read an IDENTIFIER from the string table in DATA_IN using input
55 block IB. */
56
57static tree
58input_identifier (struct data_in *data_in, struct lto_input_block *ib)
59{
60 unsigned int len;
61 const char *ptr;
62
63 ptr = streamer_read_indexed_string (data_in, ib, &len);
64 if (!ptr)
65 return NULL;
66 return get_identifier_with_length (ptr, len);
67}
68
69
70/* Read a chain of tree nodes from input block IB. DATA_IN contains
71 tables and descriptors for the file being read. */
72
73tree
74streamer_read_chain (struct lto_input_block *ib, struct data_in *data_in)
75{
76 tree first, prev, curr;
77
78 /* The chain is written as NULL terminated list of trees. */
79 first = prev = NULL_TREE;
80 do
81 {
82 curr = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
83 if (prev)
84 TREE_CHAIN (prev) = curr;
85 else
86 first = curr;
87
88 prev = curr;
89 }
90 while (curr);
91
92 return first;
93}

96/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_BASE structure of
97 expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
98
99static inline void
100unpack_ts_base_value_fields (struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
101{
102 /* Note that the code for EXPR has already been unpacked to create EXPR in
103 streamer_alloc_tree. */
104 if (!TYPE_P (expr))
105 {
106 TREE_SIDE_EFFECTS (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
107 TREE_CONSTANT (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
108 TREE_READONLY (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
109
110 /* TREE_PUBLIC is used on types to indicate that the type
111 has a TYPE_CACHED_VALUES vector. This is not streamed out,
112 so we skip it here. */
113 TREE_PUBLIC (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
114 }
115 else
116 bp_unpack_value (bp, 4);
117 TREE_ADDRESSABLE (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
118 TREE_THIS_VOLATILE (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
119 if (DECL_P (expr))
120 {
121 DECL_UNSIGNED (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
122 DECL_NAMELESS (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
123 }
124 else if (TYPE_P (expr))
125 TYPE_UNSIGNED (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
126 else
127 bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
128 TREE_ASM_WRITTEN (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
129 if (TYPE_P (expr))
130 TYPE_ARTIFICIAL (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
131 else
132 TREE_NO_WARNING (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
133 TREE_NOTHROW (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
134 TREE_STATIC (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
135 if (TREE_CODE (expr) != TREE_BINFO)
136 TREE_PRIVATE (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
137 else
138 bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
139 TREE_PROTECTED (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
140 TREE_DEPRECATED (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
141 if (TYPE_P (expr))
142 {
143 if (AGGREGATE_TYPE_P (expr))
144 TYPE_REVERSE_STORAGE_ORDER (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
145 else
146 TYPE_SATURATING (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
147 TYPE_ADDR_SPACE (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 8);
148 }
149 else if (TREE_CODE (expr) == BIT_FIELD_REF || TREE_CODE (expr) == MEM_REF)
150 {
151 REF_REVERSE_STORAGE_ORDER (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
152 bp_unpack_value (bp, 8);
153 }
154 else if (TREE_CODE (expr) == SSA_NAME)
155 {
156 SSA_NAME_IS_DEFAULT_DEF (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
157 bp_unpack_value (bp, 8);
158 }
159 else
160 bp_unpack_value (bp, 9);
161}

164/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_INT_CST structure of
165 expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
166
167static void
168unpack_ts_int_cst_value_fields (struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
169{
170 int i;
171 for (i = 0; i < TREE_INT_CST_EXT_NUNITS (expr); i++)
172 TREE_INT_CST_ELT (expr, i) = bp_unpack_var_len_int (bp);
173}
174
175
176/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_REAL_CST structure of
177 expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
178
179static void
180unpack_ts_real_cst_value_fields (struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
181{
182 unsigned i;
183 REAL_VALUE_TYPE r;
184 REAL_VALUE_TYPE *rp;
185
186 /* Clear all bits of the real value type so that we can later do
187 bitwise comparisons to see if two values are the same. */
188 memset (&r, 0, sizeof r);
189 r.cl = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 2);
190 r.decimal = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
191 r.sign = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
192 r.signalling = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
193 r.canonical = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
194 r.uexp = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, EXP_BITS);
195 for (i = 0; i < SIGSZ; i++)
196 r.sig[i] = (unsigned long) bp_unpack_value (bp, HOST_BITS_PER_LONG);
197
198 rp = ggc_alloc<real_value> ();
199 memcpy (rp, &r, sizeof (REAL_VALUE_TYPE));
200 TREE_REAL_CST_PTR (expr) = rp;
201}

204/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_FIXED_CST structure of
205 expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
206
207static void
208unpack_ts_fixed_cst_value_fields (struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
209{
210 FIXED_VALUE_TYPE *fp = ggc_alloc<fixed_value> ();
211 fp->mode = bp_unpack_machine_mode (bp);
212 fp->data.low = bp_unpack_var_len_int (bp);
213 fp->data.high = bp_unpack_var_len_int (bp);
214 TREE_FIXED_CST_PTR (expr) = fp;
215}

217/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_DECL_COMMON structure
218 of expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
219
220static void
221unpack_ts_decl_common_value_fields (struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
222{
223 SET_DECL_MODE (expr, bp_unpack_machine_mode (bp));
224 DECL_NONLOCAL (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
225 DECL_VIRTUAL_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
226 DECL_IGNORED_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
227 DECL_ABSTRACT_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
228 DECL_ARTIFICIAL (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
229 DECL_USER_ALIGN (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
230 DECL_PRESERVE_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
231 DECL_EXTERNAL (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
232 DECL_GIMPLE_REG_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
233 SET_DECL_ALIGN (expr, (unsigned) bp_unpack_var_len_unsigned (bp));
234#ifdef ACCEL_COMPILER
235 if (DECL_ALIGN (expr) > targetm.absolute_biggest_alignment)
236 SET_DECL_ALIGN (expr, targetm.absolute_biggest_alignment);
237#endif
238 if (TREE_CODE (expr) == LABEL_DECL)
239 {
240 EH_LANDING_PAD_NR (expr) = (int) bp_unpack_var_len_unsigned (bp);
241
242 /* Always assume an initial value of -1 for LABEL_DECL_UID to
243 force gimple_set_bb to recreate label_to_block_map. */
244 LABEL_DECL_UID (expr) = -1;
245 }
246
247 if (TREE_CODE (expr) == FIELD_DECL)
248 {
249 DECL_PACKED (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
250 DECL_NONADDRESSABLE_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
251 expr->decl_common.off_align = bp_unpack_value (bp, 8);
252 }
253
254 if (VAR_P (expr))
255 {
256 DECL_HAS_DEBUG_EXPR_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
257 DECL_NONLOCAL_FRAME (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
258 }
259
260 if (TREE_CODE (expr) == RESULT_DECL
261 || TREE_CODE (expr) == PARM_DECL
262 || VAR_P (expr))
263 {
264 DECL_BY_REFERENCE (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
265 if (VAR_P (expr) || TREE_CODE (expr) == PARM_DECL)
266 DECL_HAS_VALUE_EXPR_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
267 }
268}

271/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_DECL_WRTL structure
272 of expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
273
274static void
275unpack_ts_decl_wrtl_value_fields (struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
276{
277 DECL_REGISTER (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);

281/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_DECL_WITH_VIS structure
282 of expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
283
284static void
285unpack_ts_decl_with_vis_value_fields (struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
286{
287 DECL_COMMON (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
288 DECL_DLLIMPORT_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
289 DECL_WEAK (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
290 DECL_SEEN_IN_BIND_EXPR_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
291 DECL_COMDAT (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
292 DECL_VISIBILITY (expr) = (enum symbol_visibility) bp_unpack_value (bp, 2);
293 DECL_VISIBILITY_SPECIFIED (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
294
295 if (VAR_P (expr))
296 {
297 DECL_HARD_REGISTER (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
298 DECL_IN_CONSTANT_POOL (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
299 }
300
301 if (TREE_CODE (expr) == FUNCTION_DECL)
302 {
303 DECL_FINAL_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
304 DECL_CXX_CONSTRUCTOR_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
305 DECL_CXX_DESTRUCTOR_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
306 }
307}

310/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_FUNCTION_DECL structure
311 of expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
312
313static void
314unpack_ts_function_decl_value_fields (struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
315{
316 DECL_BUILT_IN_CLASS (expr) = bp_unpack_enum (bp, built_in_class,
317 BUILT_IN_LAST);
318 DECL_STATIC_CONSTRUCTOR (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
319 DECL_STATIC_DESTRUCTOR (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
320 DECL_UNINLINABLE (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
321 DECL_POSSIBLY_INLINED (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
322 DECL_IS_NOVOPS (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
323 DECL_IS_RETURNS_TWICE (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
324 DECL_IS_MALLOC (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
325 DECL_IS_OPERATOR_NEW (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
326 DECL_DECLARED_INLINE_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
327 DECL_STATIC_CHAIN (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
328 DECL_NO_INLINE_WARNING_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
329 DECL_NO_INSTRUMENT_FUNCTION_ENTRY_EXIT (expr)
330 = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
331 DECL_NO_LIMIT_STACK (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
332 DECL_DISREGARD_INLINE_LIMITS (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
333 DECL_PURE_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
334 DECL_LOOPING_CONST_OR_PURE_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
335 if (DECL_BUILT_IN_CLASS (expr) != NOT_BUILT_IN)
336 {
337 DECL_FUNCTION_CODE (expr) = (enum built_in_function) bp_unpack_value (bp,
338 12);
339 if (DECL_BUILT_IN_CLASS (expr) == BUILT_IN_NORMAL
340 && DECL_FUNCTION_CODE (expr) >= END_BUILTINS)
341 fatal_error (input_location,
342 "machine independent builtin code out of range");
343 else if (DECL_BUILT_IN_CLASS (expr) == BUILT_IN_MD)
344 {
345 tree result = targetm.builtin_decl (DECL_FUNCTION_CODE (expr), true);
346 if (!result || result == error_mark_node)
347 fatal_error (input_location,
348 "target specific builtin not available");
349 }
350 }
351}

354/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_TYPE_COMMON structure
355 of expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
356
357static void
358unpack_ts_type_common_value_fields (struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
359{
360 machine_mode mode;
361
362 mode = bp_unpack_machine_mode (bp);
363 SET_TYPE_MODE (expr, mode);
364 TYPE_STRING_FLAG (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
365 /* TYPE_NO_FORCE_BLK is private to stor-layout and need
366 no streaming. */
367 TYPE_NEEDS_CONSTRUCTING (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
368 TYPE_PACKED (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
369 TYPE_RESTRICT (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
370 TYPE_USER_ALIGN (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
371 TYPE_READONLY (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
372 if (RECORD_OR_UNION_TYPE_P (expr))
373 {
374 TYPE_TRANSPARENT_AGGR (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
375 TYPE_FINAL_P (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
376 }
377 else if (TREE_CODE (expr) == ARRAY_TYPE)
378 TYPE_NONALIASED_COMPONENT (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
379 if (AGGREGATE_TYPE_P (expr))
380 TYPE_TYPELESS_STORAGE (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
381 TYPE_PRECISION (expr) = bp_unpack_var_len_unsigned (bp);
382 SET_TYPE_ALIGN (expr, bp_unpack_var_len_unsigned (bp));
383#ifdef ACCEL_COMPILER
384 if (TYPE_ALIGN (expr) > targetm.absolute_biggest_alignment)
385 SET_TYPE_ALIGN (expr, targetm.absolute_biggest_alignment);
386#endif
387}

390/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_BLOCK structure
391 of expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
392
393static void
394unpack_ts_block_value_fields (struct data_in *data_in,
395 struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
396{
397 BLOCK_ABSTRACT (expr) = (unsigned) bp_unpack_value (bp, 1);
398 /* BLOCK_NUMBER is recomputed. */
399 stream_input_location (&BLOCK_SOURCE_LOCATION (expr), bp, data_in);
400}
401
402/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_TRANSLATION_UNIT_DECL
403 structure of expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
404
405static void
406unpack_ts_translation_unit_decl_value_fields (struct data_in *data_in,
407 struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
408{
409 TRANSLATION_UNIT_LANGUAGE (expr) = xstrdup (bp_unpack_string (data_in, bp));
410 vec_safe_push (all_translation_units, expr);
411}

413
414/* Unpack all the non-pointer fields of the TS_OMP_CLAUSE
415 structure of expression EXPR from bitpack BP. */
416
417static void
418unpack_ts_omp_clause_value_fields (struct data_in *data_in,
419 struct bitpack_d *bp, tree expr)
420{
421 stream_input_location (&OMP_CLAUSE_LOCATION (expr), bp, data_in);
422 switch (OMP_CLAUSE_CODE (expr))
423 {
424 case OMP_CLAUSE_DEFAULT:
425 OMP_CLAUSE_DEFAULT_KIND (expr)
426 = bp_unpack_enum (bp, omp_clause_default_kind,
427 OMP_CLAUSE_DEFAULT_LAST);
428 break;
429 case OMP_CLAUSE_SCHEDULE:
430 OMP_CLAUSE_SCHEDULE_KIND (expr)
431 = bp_unpack_enum (bp, omp_clause_schedule_kind,
432 OMP_CLAUSE_SCHEDULE_LAST);
433 break;
434 case OMP_CLAUSE_DEPEND:
435 OMP_CLAUSE_DEPEND_KIND (expr)
436 = bp_unpack_enum (bp, omp_clause_depend_kind, OMP_CLAUSE_DEPEND_LAST);
437 break;
438 case OMP_CLAUSE_MAP:
439 OMP_CLAUSE_SET_MAP_KIND (expr, bp_unpack_enum (bp, gomp_map_kind,
440 GOMP_MAP_LAST));
441 break;
442 case OMP_CLAUSE_PROC_BIND:
443 OMP_CLAUSE_PROC_BIND_KIND (expr)
444 = bp_unpack_enum (bp, omp_clause_proc_bind_kind,
445 OMP_CLAUSE_PROC_BIND_LAST);
446 break;
447 case OMP_CLAUSE_REDUCTION:
448 OMP_CLAUSE_REDUCTION_CODE (expr)
449 = bp_unpack_enum (bp, tree_code, MAX_TREE_CODES);
450 break;
451 default:
452 break;
453 }
454}

457/* Read all the language-independent bitfield values for EXPR from IB.
458 Return the partially unpacked bitpack so the caller can unpack any other
459 bitfield values that the writer may have written. */
460
461void
462streamer_read_tree_bitfields (struct lto_input_block *ib,
463 struct data_in *data_in, tree expr)
464{
465 enum tree_code code;
466 struct bitpack_d bp;
467
468 /* Read the bitpack of non-pointer values from IB. */
469 bp = streamer_read_bitpack (ib);
470
471 /* The first word in BP contains the code of the tree that we
472 are about to read. */
473 code = (enum tree_code) bp_unpack_value (&bp, 16);
474 lto_tag_check (lto_tree_code_to_tag (code),
475 lto_tree_code_to_tag (TREE_CODE (expr)));
476
477 /* Note that all these functions are highly sensitive to changes in
478 the types and sizes of each of the fields being packed. */
479 unpack_ts_base_value_fields (&bp, expr);
480
481 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_INT_CST))
482 unpack_ts_int_cst_value_fields (&bp, expr);
483
484 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_REAL_CST))
485 unpack_ts_real_cst_value_fields (&bp, expr);
486
487 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_FIXED_CST))
488 unpack_ts_fixed_cst_value_fields (&bp, expr);
489
490 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_DECL_MINIMAL))
491 stream_input_location (&DECL_SOURCE_LOCATION (expr), &bp, data_in);
492
493 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_DECL_COMMON))
494 unpack_ts_decl_common_value_fields (&bp, expr);
495
496 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_DECL_WRTL))
497 unpack_ts_decl_wrtl_value_fields (&bp, expr);
498
499 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_DECL_WITH_VIS))
500 unpack_ts_decl_with_vis_value_fields (&bp, expr);
501
502 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_FUNCTION_DECL))
503 unpack_ts_function_decl_value_fields (&bp, expr);
504
505 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_TYPE_COMMON))
506 unpack_ts_type_common_value_fields (&bp, expr);
507
508 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_EXP))
509 {
510 stream_input_location (&EXPR_CHECK (expr)->exp.locus, &bp, data_in);
511 if (code == MEM_REF
512 || code == TARGET_MEM_REF)
513 {
514 MR_DEPENDENCE_CLIQUE (expr)
515 = (unsigned)bp_unpack_value (&bp, sizeof (short) * 8);
516 if (MR_DEPENDENCE_CLIQUE (expr) != 0)
517 MR_DEPENDENCE_BASE (expr)
518 = (unsigned)bp_unpack_value (&bp, sizeof (short) * 8);
519 }
520 }
521
522 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_BLOCK))
523 unpack_ts_block_value_fields (data_in, &bp, expr);
524
525 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_TRANSLATION_UNIT_DECL))
526 unpack_ts_translation_unit_decl_value_fields (data_in, &bp, expr);
527
528 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_OPTIMIZATION))
529 cl_optimization_stream_in (&bp, TREE_OPTIMIZATION (expr));
530
531 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_BINFO))
532 {
533 unsigned HOST_WIDE_INT length = bp_unpack_var_len_unsigned (&bp);
534 if (length > 0)
535 vec_safe_grow (BINFO_BASE_ACCESSES (expr), length);
536 }
537
538 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_CONSTRUCTOR))
539 {
540 unsigned HOST_WIDE_INT length = bp_unpack_var_len_unsigned (&bp);
541 if (length > 0)
542 vec_safe_grow (CONSTRUCTOR_ELTS (expr), length);
543 }
544
545#ifndef ACCEL_COMPILER
546 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_TARGET_OPTION))
547 {
548 cl_target_option_stream_in (data_in, &bp, TREE_TARGET_OPTION (expr));
549 if (targetm.target_option.post_stream_in)
550 targetm.target_option.post_stream_in (TREE_TARGET_OPTION (expr));
551 }
552#endif
553
554 if (code == OMP_CLAUSE)
555 unpack_ts_omp_clause_value_fields (data_in, &bp, expr);
556}

558
559/* Materialize a new tree from input block IB using descriptors in
560 DATA_IN. The code for the new tree should match TAG. Store in
561 *IX_P the index into the reader cache where the new tree is stored. */
562
563tree
564streamer_alloc_tree (struct lto_input_block *ib, struct data_in *data_in,
565 enum LTO_tags tag)
566{
567 enum tree_code code;
568 tree result;
569#ifdef LTO_STREAMER_DEBUG
570 HOST_WIDE_INT orig_address_in_writer;
571#endif
572
573 result = NULL_TREE;
574
575#ifdef LTO_STREAMER_DEBUG
576 /* Read the word representing the memory address for the tree
577 as it was written by the writer. This is useful when
578 debugging differences between the writer and reader. */
579 orig_address_in_writer = streamer_read_hwi (ib);
580 gcc_assert ((intptr_t) orig_address_in_writer == orig_address_in_writer);
581#endif
582
583 code = lto_tag_to_tree_code (tag);
584
585 /* We should never see an SSA_NAME tree. Only the version numbers of
586 SSA names are ever written out. See input_ssa_names. */
587 gcc_assert (code != SSA_NAME);
588
589 /* Instantiate a new tree using the header data. */
590 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_STRING))
591 result = streamer_read_string_cst (data_in, ib);
592 else if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_IDENTIFIER))
593 result = input_identifier (data_in, ib);
594 else if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_VEC))
595 {
596 HOST_WIDE_INT len = streamer_read_hwi (ib);
597 result = make_tree_vec (len);
598 }
599 else if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_VECTOR))
600 {
601 HOST_WIDE_INT len = streamer_read_hwi (ib);
602 result = make_vector (len);
603 }
604 else if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_BINFO))
605 {
606 unsigned HOST_WIDE_INT len = streamer_read_uhwi (ib);
607 result = make_tree_binfo (len);
608 }
609 else if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_INT_CST))
610 {
611 unsigned HOST_WIDE_INT len = streamer_read_uhwi (ib);
612 unsigned HOST_WIDE_INT ext_len = streamer_read_uhwi (ib);
613 result = make_int_cst (len, ext_len);
614 }
615 else if (code == CALL_EXPR)
616 {
617 unsigned HOST_WIDE_INT nargs = streamer_read_uhwi (ib);
618 return build_vl_exp (CALL_EXPR, nargs + 3);
619 }
620 else if (code == OMP_CLAUSE)
621 {
622 enum omp_clause_code subcode
623 = (enum omp_clause_code) streamer_read_uhwi (ib);
624 return build_omp_clause (UNKNOWN_LOCATION, subcode);
625 }
626 else
627 {
628 /* For all other nodes, materialize the tree with a raw
629 make_node call. */
630 result = make_node (code);
631 }
632
633#ifdef LTO_STREAMER_DEBUG
634 /* Store the original address of the tree as seen by the writer
635 in RESULT's aux field. This is useful when debugging streaming
636 problems. This way, a debugging session can be started on
637 both writer and reader with a breakpoint using this address
638 value in both. */
639 lto_orig_address_map (result, (intptr_t) orig_address_in_writer);
640#endif
641
642 return result;
643}

700/* Read all pointer fields in the TS_DECL_COMMON structure of EXPR from
701 input block IB. DATA_IN contains tables and descriptors for the
702 file being read. */
703
704static void
705lto_input_ts_decl_common_tree_pointers (struct lto_input_block *ib,
706 struct data_in *data_in, tree expr)
707{
708 DECL_SIZE (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
709 DECL_SIZE_UNIT (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
710 DECL_ATTRIBUTES (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
711
712 /* Do not stream DECL_ABSTRACT_ORIGIN. We cannot handle debug information
713 for early inlining so drop it on the floor instead of ICEing in
714 dwarf2out.c. */
715

717 && DECL_HAS_VALUE_EXPR_P (expr))
718 SET_DECL_VALUE_EXPR (expr, stream_read_tree (ib, data_in));
719
720 if (VAR_P (expr))
721 {
722 tree dexpr = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
723 if (dexpr)
724 SET_DECL_DEBUG_EXPR (expr, dexpr);
725 }
726}

796 if (DECL_FUNCTION_PERSONALITY (expr))
797 lto_init_eh ();

801/* Read all pointer fields in the TS_TYPE_COMMON structure of EXPR from
802 input block IB. DATA_IN contains tables and descriptors for the file
803 being read. */
804
805static void
806lto_input_ts_type_common_tree_pointers (struct lto_input_block *ib,
807 struct data_in *data_in, tree expr)
808{
809 TYPE_SIZE (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
810 TYPE_SIZE_UNIT (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
811 TYPE_ATTRIBUTES (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
812 TYPE_NAME (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
813 /* Do not stream TYPE_POINTER_TO or TYPE_REFERENCE_TO. They will be
814 reconstructed during fixup. */
815 /* Do not stream TYPE_NEXT_VARIANT, we reconstruct the variant lists
816 during fixup. */
817 TYPE_MAIN_VARIANT (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
818 TYPE_CONTEXT (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
819 /* TYPE_CANONICAL gets re-computed during type merging. */
820 TYPE_CANONICAL (expr) = NULL_TREE;
821 TYPE_STUB_DECL (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
822}
823
824/* Read all pointer fields in the TS_TYPE_NON_COMMON structure of EXPR
825 from input block IB. DATA_IN contains tables and descriptors for the
826 file being read. */
827
828static void
829lto_input_ts_type_non_common_tree_pointers (struct lto_input_block *ib,
830 struct data_in *data_in,
831 tree expr)
832{
833 if (TREE_CODE (expr) == ENUMERAL_TYPE)
834 TYPE_VALUES (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
835 else if (TREE_CODE (expr) == ARRAY_TYPE)
836 TYPE_DOMAIN (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
837 else if (RECORD_OR_UNION_TYPE_P (expr))
838 TYPE_FIELDS (expr) = streamer_read_chain (ib, data_in);
839 else if (TREE_CODE (expr) == FUNCTION_TYPE
840 || TREE_CODE (expr) == METHOD_TYPE)
841 TYPE_ARG_TYPES (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
842
843 if (!POINTER_TYPE_P (expr))
844 TYPE_MINVAL (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
845 TYPE_MAXVAL (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
846 if (RECORD_OR_UNION_TYPE_P (expr))
847 TYPE_BINFO (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
848}

882/* Read all pointer fields in the TS_EXP structure of EXPR from input
883 block IB. DATA_IN contains tables and descriptors for the
884 file being read. */
885
886
887static void
888lto_input_ts_exp_tree_pointers (struct lto_input_block *ib,
889 struct data_in *data_in, tree expr)
890{
891 int i;
892 tree block;
893
894 for (i = 0; i < TREE_OPERAND_LENGTH (expr); i++)
895 TREE_OPERAND (expr, i) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
896
897 block = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
898
899 /* TODO: Block is stored in the locus information. It may make more sense to
900 to make it go via the location cache. */
901 if (block)
902 {
903 data_in->location_cache.apply_location_cache ();
904 TREE_SET_BLOCK (expr, block);
905 }
906}

909/* Read all pointer fields in the TS_BLOCK structure of EXPR from input
910 block IB. DATA_IN contains tables and descriptors for the
911 file being read. */
912
913static void
914lto_input_ts_block_tree_pointers (struct lto_input_block *ib,
915 struct data_in *data_in, tree expr)
916{
917 BLOCK_VARS (expr) = streamer_read_chain (ib, data_in);
918
919 BLOCK_SUPERCONTEXT (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
920
921 /* Stream BLOCK_ABSTRACT_ORIGIN and BLOCK_SOURCE_LOCATION for
922 the limited cases we can handle - those that represent inlined
923 function scopes. For the rest them on the floor instead of ICEing in
924 dwarf2out.c. */
925 BLOCK_ABSTRACT_ORIGIN (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
926 /* Do not stream BLOCK_NONLOCALIZED_VARS. We cannot handle debug information
927 for early inlined BLOCKs so drop it on the floor instead of ICEing in
928 dwarf2out.c. */
929
930 /* BLOCK_FRAGMENT_ORIGIN and BLOCK_FRAGMENT_CHAIN is not live at LTO
931 streaming time. */
932
933 /* We re-compute BLOCK_SUBBLOCKS of our parent here instead
934 of streaming it. For non-BLOCK BLOCK_SUPERCONTEXTs we still
935 stream the child relationship explicitly. */
936 if (BLOCK_SUPERCONTEXT (expr)
937 && TREE_CODE (BLOCK_SUPERCONTEXT (expr)) == BLOCK)
938 {
939 BLOCK_CHAIN (expr) = BLOCK_SUBBLOCKS (BLOCK_SUPERCONTEXT (expr));
940 BLOCK_SUBBLOCKS (BLOCK_SUPERCONTEXT (expr)) = expr;
941 }
942
943 /* The global block is rooted at the TU decl. Hook it here to
944 avoid the need to stream in this block during WPA time. */
945 else if (BLOCK_SUPERCONTEXT (expr)
946 && TREE_CODE (BLOCK_SUPERCONTEXT (expr)) == TRANSLATION_UNIT_DECL)
947 DECL_INITIAL (BLOCK_SUPERCONTEXT (expr)) = expr;
948
949 /* The function-level block is connected at the time we read in
950 function bodies for the same reason. */
951}
952
953
954/* Read all pointer fields in the TS_BINFO structure of EXPR from input
955 block IB. DATA_IN contains tables and descriptors for the
956 file being read. */
957
958static void
959lto_input_ts_binfo_tree_pointers (struct lto_input_block *ib,
960 struct data_in *data_in, tree expr)
961{
962 unsigned i;
963 tree t;
964
965 /* Note that the number of slots in EXPR was read in
966 streamer_alloc_tree when instantiating EXPR. However, the
967 vector is empty so we cannot rely on vec::length to know how many
968 elements to read. So, this list is emitted as a 0-terminated
969 list on the writer side. */
970 do
971 {
972 t = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
973 if (t)
974 BINFO_BASE_BINFOS (expr)->quick_push (t);
975 }
976 while (t);
977
978 BINFO_OFFSET (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
979 BINFO_VTABLE (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
980 BINFO_VPTR_FIELD (expr) = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
981
982 /* The vector of BINFO_BASE_ACCESSES is pre-allocated during
983 unpacking the bitfield section. */
984 for (i = 0; i < vec_safe_length (BINFO_BASE_ACCESSES (expr)); i++)
985 {
986 tree a = stream_read_tree (ib, data_in);
987 (*BINFO_BASE_ACCESSES (expr))[i] = a;
988 }
989 /* Do not walk BINFO_INHERITANCE_CHAIN, BINFO_SUBVTT_INDEX
990 and BINFO_VPTR_INDEX; these are used by C++ FE only. */
991}

998static void
999lto_input_ts_constructor_tree_pointers (struct lto_input_block *ib,
1000 struct data_in *data_in, tree expr)

1003

1030/* Read all pointer fields in EXPR from input block IB. DATA_IN
1031 contains tables and descriptors for the file being read. */
1032
1033void
1034streamer_read_tree_body (struct lto_input_block *ib, struct data_in *data_in,
1035 tree expr)
1036{
1037 enum tree_code code;
1038
1039 code = TREE_CODE (expr);
1040
1041 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_TYPED))
1042 lto_input_ts_common_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1043
1044 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_VECTOR))
1045 lto_input_ts_vector_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1046
1047 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_COMPLEX))
1048 lto_input_ts_complex_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1049
1050 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_DECL_MINIMAL))
1051 lto_input_ts_decl_minimal_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1052
1053 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_DECL_COMMON))
1054 lto_input_ts_decl_common_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1055
1056 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_DECL_NON_COMMON))
1057 lto_input_ts_decl_non_common_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1058
1059 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_DECL_WITH_VIS))
1060 lto_input_ts_decl_with_vis_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1061
1062 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_FIELD_DECL))
1063 lto_input_ts_field_decl_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1064
1065 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_FUNCTION_DECL))
1066 lto_input_ts_function_decl_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1067
1068 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_TYPE_COMMON))
1069 lto_input_ts_type_common_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1070
1071 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_TYPE_NON_COMMON))
1072 lto_input_ts_type_non_common_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1073
1074 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_LIST))
1075 lto_input_ts_list_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1076
1077 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_VEC))
1078 lto_input_ts_vec_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1079
1080 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_EXP))
1081 lto_input_ts_exp_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1082
1083 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_BLOCK))
1084 lto_input_ts_block_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1085
1086 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_BINFO))
1087 lto_input_ts_binfo_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1088
1089 if (CODE_CONTAINS_STRUCT (code, TS_CONSTRUCTOR))
1090 lto_input_ts_constructor_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1091
1092 if (code == OMP_CLAUSE)
1093 lto_input_ts_omp_clause_tree_pointers (ib, data_in, expr);
1094}

1096
1097/* Read an index IX from input block IB and return the tree node at
1098 DATA_IN->FILE_DATA->GLOBALS_INDEX[IX]. */
1099
1100tree
1101streamer_get_pickled_tree (struct lto_input_block *ib, struct data_in *data_in)
1102{
1103 unsigned HOST_WIDE_INT ix;
1104 tree result;
1105 enum LTO_tags expected_tag;
1106
1107 ix = streamer_read_uhwi (ib);
1108 expected_tag = streamer_read_enum (ib, LTO_tags, LTO_NUM_TAGS);
1109
1110 result = streamer_tree_cache_get_tree (data_in->reader_cache, ix);
1111 gcc_assert (result
1112 && TREE_CODE (result) == lto_tag_to_tree_code (expected_tag));
1113
1114 return result;
1115}
